text: Orangeburg, also known as The Garden City, is a principal city in and the county seat of Orangeburg County, South Carolina, United States. The population of the city was 13,240 according to the 2020 United States Census. The city is located 37 miles southeast of Columbia. The city is located 72 miles from Charleston. ==References== Category:Cities in South Carolina Category:County seats in South Carolina
title: Orangeburg, South Carolina
